room_title: Escape room "The Deadly Virus" by The Rooms of BCS in College Station
room_description: Millions of people across the world have been infected with a life-threatening virus. Dr. Lawerence Jensen from Care Pharmaceuticals was working on a cure that could save lives across the globe. He has just recently died, presumably from the very disease he was trying to cure. You and your team have been tasked with looking into the death of Dr. Jensen. What you learn will put you and your friends at risk, as you shed light on a larger conspiracy.
